thread.title: Soleil
thread.title_full: Blinds on the Net reviewed by Soleil

author: Soleil
title: Soleil
text: We are in Perth where it is not always easy to get access to fast and reasonable priced goods. Blinds on the net were great, it was fast (10days) from "made to measure" order to delivery, the quality is good, the staff pleasant to talk to and happy to give some advices. We placed 2 separate orders and we have been very happy with their services so far!! Highly recommended!
